{"type": "article", "id": 4776, "title": "Paolino 收纳工具", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-29T07:21:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233615k2nO6S7DGKATlZzW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tPaolino 是由意大利设计工作室 Sovrappensiero 开发的一款收纳工具，它有点像是文件收纳盒与纸镇的结合体，整体非常轻薄，由两片经镭射切割的重叠金属片结合而成，侧面轮廓看起来非常利落简洁，而中间附有一个将整体结构水平垂直切开的双 T 型架桥，可随着堆叠的文件的多少进行高度调整。整体颜色的搭配亦非常柔和清新。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233613RBifuyM9EDnVGNKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233613YdZ04gQWBhvsEVJ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233614wDJ9oZWdGAafmv1Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233614By2jYcS7u35PKrVo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233615YczD8iIFWUQs24bE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}